    <briefdescription>
<para>Structure describing a I2C device on I3C bus. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Instances of this are passed to the I3C controller device APIs, for example: () i3c_i2c_device_register() to tell the controller of an I2C device. () i3c_i2c_transfers() to initiate data transfers between controller and I2C device.</para>
<para>Fields other than <computeroutput>node</computeroutput> must be initialized by the module that implements the device behavior prior to passing the object reference to I3C controller device APIs. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
